# Grunder kanon (tre sanningsslager)

Before claiming a Grunder slide (G01–G52) is **live**, classify evidence into exactly one layer.

## Layer 1 — Runtime kanon (implementerat / delvis i kod)

| Source | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| `.context/*.md` (especially `security.md`, `arkiv-minne.md`) | Architecture, silos, Sacred Features |
| `firestore.rules` | WORM, owner-bound collections |
| `functions/src/sharedRules.ts` | Agent prompts — **only** allowed prompt source |
| `functions/src/agents/`, `functions/src/adk/` | DCAP, Kompis, cards, synapses |

**Confirmed runtime (U1–U5, 2026-05-22):** DCAP before LLM; three silos; Gräns-Arkitekten; BIFF at high risk; Zero Footprint + Kill Switch; Drive → `kb_docs`; 10 cards / 2 executors; Barnen routing + PA appendix. See [`docs/archive/evaluations-2026-05/GRUNDER-UTVARDERING-RESULTAT.md`](../../docs/archive/evaluations-2026-05/GRUNDER-UTVARDERING-RESULTAT.md).

## Layer 2 — Spec / GAP (planned, not live until coded)

| Source | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| `docs/specs/modules/*-SPEC.md` | Module intent, appendices |
| `docs/specs/modules/Arkiv-GAP-REGISTER.md` | Open gaps — do not treat as shipped |

Label claims as **GAP** or **spec-only** until Layer 1 evidence exists.

## Layer 3 — Grunder slides (vision / rejected)

| Source | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| [`docs/specs/modules/grunder-slides/INVENTAR.md`](../../docs/specs/modules/grunder-slides/INVENTAR.md) | Per-slide status: implementerat · delvis · vision-only · **avvisat** |

**Slides are not runtime proof.** A PNG/PDF slide does not mean the feature exists in prod.

### Avvisat — never implement

| G | Item |
|---|------|
| **G05** | Cirkulär MåBra flow-vy |
| **G42** | Plant / gamification i offentligt lager |

### Vision-only — do not migrate without explicit `kör [GAP]`

| G | Topic |
|---|--------|
| **G01** | Dotprompt — separera logik från kod |
| **G28** | Supervisor + Firebase Genkit |
| **G29** | Dotprompts som IaC |
| **G33** | Stateless backend via Genkit (partial overlap — keep ADK as runtime) |

**Do not start:** Genkit/Dotprompt migration, `.prompt` files, or replacing `sharedRules.ts` with slide-only architecture.

### INVENTAR summary (Fas A)

- **implementerat:** 2 (e.g. G35 RBAC, G48 tre silor)
- **delvis:** 18
- **vision-only:** 30
- **avvisat:** 2 (G05, G42)

When a slide is **delvis**, describe what exists in Layer 1 and what remains in Layer 2 — never imply full slide coverage.

## Runtime changes from Grunder

- Allowed only when user says **`kör [GAP]`** or a tracked item in `Arkiv-GAP-REGISTER.md`.
- Re-run read-only check `kör grunder U1` … `U5` after major agent/security PRs (see evaluation doc).

